cted. The higher the overall score, the better!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618210/extras/9a0d53bd8de2b08e1e4e15809fb96759.poster.avif?t=1760416589\" width=610 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618210/extras/9a0d53bd8de2b08e1e4e15809fb96759.webm?t=1760416589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618210/extras/9a0d53bd8de2b08e1e4e15809fb96759.mp4?t=1760416589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
